SIMPLE: propagable
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Propagable
<hw>Prop"a*ga*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Propagate</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Capable of being propagated, or of being continued
or multiplied by natural generation or production.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Capable of being spread or extended by any means; --
said of tenets, doctrines, or principles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Propaganda</ent>⟦br⟧
